320
00:23:29,208 --> 00:23:30,875
I'm sorry, Mom.

321
00:23:30,958 --> 00:23:34,166
I had no idea
your job was so rough.

322
00:23:34,250 --> 00:23:37,083
I don't want you to work
so hard anymore.

323
00:23:37,166 --> 00:23:39,791
And please, don't worry
about money either.

324
00:23:39,875 --> 00:23:42,166
Miss Mariko said
she'd give me half the profits

325
00:23:42,250 --> 00:23:44,791
from any food
I sell in her café.

326
00:23:44,875 --> 00:23:47,000
Maybe if we save
the money I make,

327
00:23:47,083 --> 00:23:49,250
we can build
our own house someday.

328
00:23:49,333 --> 00:23:51,250
Like we've always wanted.

329
00:23:51,333 --> 00:23:55,291
But right now, Mom,
you just need to get better.

